  "title": "[searchBox] Powered by",
  "body": "Based on this issue ( https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/25 ), I'm not sure anymore that the search input will be a widget, but if it is, it could be great to embed the \"Powered by\" with it, enabled by default.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
